---
title: Slow-Cooked Pork Ramen-Style Noodle Soup with Soft Boiled Egg
description: Do you love ramen as much as we do? How could you not - tender pork and noodles swimming around together in a hot, savoury broth and topped with a perfectly jammy egg. This one’s super easy to make as well, the meat gets the rich flavour in your slow cooker, you just need to quickly boil the eggs and noodles for a feast in a bowl!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
